    "path": "/posts/2023-01-11--How-to-test-library-using-private-registry/how-to-test-library-using-private-registry",
    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"642112e5-9229-57a1-bd05-e147cf115b91","html":"<p>I recently need a private npm registry for testing a standalone library before publishing it to npm.</p>\n<p>Verdaccio came to mind - I recall it is introduced via a framework publish showcase.\nVerdaccio is a simple, zero-config-required local private npm registry.</p>\n<h2 id=\"install-verdaccio\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#install-verdaccio\" aria-label=\"install verdaccio permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Install Verdaccio</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> global <span class=\"token function\">add</span> verdaccio@6-next</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"start-it\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#start-it\" aria-label=\"start it permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Start it</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">verdaccio</code></pre></div>\n<p>Visit <a href=\"http://localhost:4873/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">http://localhost:4873/</a>.</p>\n<p>This is the private registry</p>\n<h2 id=\"create-user\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#create-user\" aria-label=\"create user permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Create user</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> adduser --registry http://localhost:4873</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"publish\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#publish\" aria-label=\"publish permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Publish</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> publish --registry http://localhost:4873</code></pre></div>\n<p>Visit <a href=\"http://localhost:4873/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">http://localhost:4873/</a>.</p>\n<p>Verify the node module has been published</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm link</code> is also very convenient for testing the library before publish.</p>\n<p>But it cannot completely simulate the production ENV.</p>\n<p>I would suggest using Verdaccio afterwards.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>Happy new year!!!</p>\n<p>I haven’t publish anything in last two month because some life updates.</p>\n<p>I feel very energized about updating my blog again.</p>\n<p>I’m currently sitting in a warm apartment.</p>\n<p>Fresh air, unblocked internet and sparkling water perfectly fit in.</p>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/2023-01-11--How-to-test-library-using-private-registry/how-to-test-library-using-private-registry","tagSlugs":["/tag/frontend/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2023-01-11T12:40:32.169Z","description":"","tags":["Frontend"],"title":"How to test library using private registry","socialImage":""}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/2023-01-11--How-to-test-library-using-private-registry/how-to-test-library-using-private-registry"}},
